{"tid":1570343,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE 英文／通識 免費改文！","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:02:04.000Z","uid":11058,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d996251a5268aa1276926457305bec388f1c11","tid":1570343,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"又開始今年既*連登限定*免費改文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">罷課不罷學</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n交文好簡單，免費<br />\n唯一代價係比我用你交既文教書！<br />\n<br />\n作左文又或者做左通識既題目之後 <br />\n可以send去awenglishls@gmail.com<br />\n我會盡快幫你改+比comments<br />\n7-14日內send翻比你 <br />\n不論Past papers或者出版社題目都可以架 <br />\n<br />\n你可以<br />\n1. send .doc/.docx比我<br />\n2. send SCAN既手寫文比我 (可以用手機dl camscanner)<br />\n(影相就唔改啦好難睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有問題都可以係到問！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：小班補習導師 主修英文 英文通識5** <br />\nig: awenglishls</span>"},{"pid":"7c03381470c6c360f1a0ba58925a99d5623ee5f1","tid":1570343,"uid":302382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"Push 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d049ba672da8b183b9652b77b0477278512c62","tid":1570343,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"支持巴打<br />\n19dse有睇過你啲po <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85768e4785adc248aad9be11347c663e9c6f592","tid":1570343,"uid":19192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29594ac1d870a9098cb7f5afe086c73c8a83fc8f","tid":1570343,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d049ba672da8b183b9652b77b047727